hopobject.body: Yes, I play the guitar clinique superbalanced makeup all shades reviews During his investigation, he found that updates made to AnTuTu seemed to favor Intel chips over ARM chips. As he explains, the updates gave ARM processors a mere 50% upgrade in performance whereas Intel chips were seeing increases of up to 292%. This is what originally piqued McGregor’s interest to look more into the situation. It was a good thing he did, too, because he was completely right.
